INGREDIENTS
2 lbs (5 cups) Beans 
1 lb carne seca 
½ pound fresh Stew meat
½ pound Bacon (thick cut)
½ pound Paio Sausages 
1 pound Portuguese Sausage (Linguiça)
½ pound Salt Pork 
2 onions Chopped 
1 teaspoon Black Pepper
2 Tomatoes (Peeled/seeded/chopped)
8 cloves Garlic crushed
2 tablespoons white wine vinegar
2 or 3 Bay leaves
